    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159180/extras/0d342440c74adf98f84638a3933fa3f7.poster.avif?t=1729020638\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159180/extras/0d342440c74adf98f84638a3933fa3f7.webm?t=1729020638\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159180/extras/6ffe13c922a22981f7063b07f69f9ae1.poster.avif?t=1729020638\" width=600 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159180/extras/6ffe13c922a22981f7063b07f69f9ae1.webm?t=1729020638\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159180/extras/6ffe13c922a22981f7063b07f69f9ae1.mp4?t=1729020638\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A game with cute creative kittens who love Halloween and go out in costumes to play trick or treats!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159180/extras/7310f97d4deae992130c7cfe2a799e89.poster.avif?t=1729020638\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159180/extras/7310f97d4deae992130c7cfe2a799e89.webm?t=1729020638\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Be amazed by the minimalist style and beautiful art of this game!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The arts of Hidden Shapes - Trick or Cats are inspired by the big day of Halloween!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159180/extras/30970520710c0dc58403cdd9cb025fb5.avif?t=1729020638\" width=584 height=287 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Relax with these cute Halloween-inspired hand-drawn jigsaw puzzles of our kittens and forget about your worries!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159180/extras/70b79996a49a7d60d4db8486ae4983b3.poster.avif?t=1729020638\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2159180/extras/70b79996a49a7d60d4db8486ae4983b3.webm?t=1729020638\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >So that you can have fun and enjoy the game more, after solving a puzzle the complete art will be released, so at any time you can have fun again solving the entire puzzle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong> - Steam Community </strong></u><strong> </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don't forget to follow us on the Steam page so you'll know about new games and news from the studio.</p>",
